#

Hearty Beef and Vegetable Chili

$30
350 kcal

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinGluten FreeLow Carb

Tags:

ChiliComfort FoodMeal PrepHeartySpicy

Description

A rich and robust chili loaded with ground beef, beans, and a medley of vegetables, perfect for cozy gatherings.

Ingredients

  • Ground beef: 6 lb
  • Canned diced tomatoes: 3 (14.5 oz) cans
  • Kidney beans: 2 (15 oz) cans
  • Black beans: 2 (15 oz) cans
  • Yellow onion: 2, chopped
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Bell peppers: 2, diced (any color)
  • Chili powder: 4 tbsp
  • Cumin: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: 1 tsp
  • Black pepper: 1 tsp
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Corn: 2 cups, frozen
  • Fresh cilantro: for garnish (optional)
